WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
Hey Ling Ling, where were you born?

00:04.000 --> 00:09.000
I was born in a small village in Chantilly Province.

00:09.000 --> 00:12.000
What was the name of the village?

00:12.000 --> 00:16.000
Hutuan, where were you born Tony?

00:16.000 --> 00:22.000
I was born in Cambridge. It's a small city in England.

00:22.000 --> 00:26.000
What was the name of your first school?

00:26.000 --> 00:29.000
It was Darwin Primary School.

00:29.000 --> 00:32.000
Who was your first teacher?

00:32.000 --> 00:36.000
My first teacher was Mrs. Lane.

00:36.000 --> 00:40.000
She was strict but very nice.

00:40.000 --> 00:43.000
Who was your first teacher?

00:43.000 --> 00:47.000
Muziao, she was very friendly.

00:47.000 --> 00:52.000
Who were your first friends? What were they like?

00:52.000 --> 00:55.000
Their names were Becky and Adam.

00:55.000 --> 00:58.000
Becky was very good in class.

00:58.000 --> 01:03.000
But Adam wasn't. He was quite difficult.

01:03.000 --> 01:08.000
And what were you like? Were you difficult in class too?

01:08.000 --> 01:13.000
No, I wasn't. I was very good.

